  LOADING SPACE CRUSADE : THE VOYAGE BEYOND 

 1. PLEASE IGNORE THE FIRST DISK AND PUT THE DISK THREE IN THE 
    BOOTDRIVE !
 2. FOLLOW ON-SCREEN INSTRUCTIONS 

  
                   GAME PLAY AND NEW OPTIONS :

 THE FOLLOWING ENHANCEMENTS HAVE BEEN MADE TO THE SPACE CRUSADE 
 MISSION DISKS IN ORDER TO IMPROVE THE GAME PLAY .

 NEW ENEMIES :

 1.SPACE OGRES. 
   THESE REPLACE THE GRETCHINS. THEY HAVE AN AMOUR
   VALUE OF TWO, CAN ONLY MOVE FOUR SQUARES, TO FIRE THEY USE ONE 
   HAVY WEAPON AND ONE LIGHT WEAPON DICE, AND IN HAND COMBAT TWO 
   HAVY WEAPONS DICES.
   POINTS FOR KILL: 10 POINTS

 2.NEW DREADNOUGHT. 
   THE DREADNOUGT MARK VII HAS REPLACES THE OLD DREADNOUGHT. 
   THE NEW DREADNOUGTH HAS THE SAME WEAPONS AS THE ORGINAL, PLUS A TOP 
   MOUNTED GRENADE WHICH CAN FRE UP TO FOUR GRENADES AT THE SAME OR 
   SEPARATE TARGETS, THE GREANDES USE TWO LIGHT WEAPON DICE. IT CAN ALSO 
   MOVE UP TO SIX SQUARES.
   POINTS FOR KILL : ORIGINAL DREADNOUGHT POINTS PLUS TEN EXTRA POINTS !

 3. VILOUS PARASITES. 
    THEY APPEAR FROM HOLES IN THE FLOOR (MARIENS CAN`T 
    STEP ON A HOLE) AND WILL CATCH ANY MARINE ON AN ADJACENT AND SUCK HIM 
    INTO THE HOLE UNLESS IT IS HIT BY A WEAPON HIT OF TWO OR ABOVE BEFOR 
    THE NEXT TURN. IF THIS HAPPENS, THE PARASITE WILL RETREAT INTO ITS
    HOLE AND THEN THE MARINE CAN MOVE. IF THE MARINE IS NOT RELEASED
    THE PARASITE WILL RETREAR HIM, AND HIS SKELETON WILL BE SPAT OUT OF 
    ANOTHER HOLE SOMEWHERE. THESE PARASITES CANNOT BE KILLED .
 
 4. SOULSUCKER QUENN, AKA THE MOTHERSUCKER.
    THIS IS A PREVIOUSLY UNSEEN ALIEN WHICH SPITS VENOM. THIS
    VENOM HAS ZHE SAME EFFECT AS A HEAVY BOLTER, AND CAN FIRE IN ANY 
    DIRECTION. THIS CREATURE ALSO HAS A TAIL WHICH CAN BE USED TO
    ATTACK MARINES ON SQUARES BEHIND HER. HAND TO HAND RULES APPLY, WITH
    THE TAIL USING TWO LIGHT WEAPON DICE. THE MOTHERSUCKER ALSO HAS CLAWS 
    WHICH CAN BE USED IN HAND TO HAND COMBAT USING TWO LIGHT WEAPON DICE
    BUT WHICH ONLY ATTACKS MARINES ON SQUARES THAT ARE IN FRONT OF HER.
    SHE DOES NOT MOVE.
    POINTS FOR KILL : 30 POINTS.
    
  NOTE TO NEW RANKS :
  
  NEW RANKS CANNOT BE LOADED INTO THE ORGINAL SPACE CRUSADE MISSIONS 
  AND THE OLD RANKS CAN NOT BE LOADED INTO THE NEW GAME !

  THE NEW RANKS ARE :
 
  1. REAR ADMIRAL.
  2. ADMIRAL.
  3. FLEET ADMIRAL.
 
  NEW WEAPONS 

  NEW COMMANDER WEAPONS 
  THE WEAPONS AVAILABLE TO A COMMANDER WILL HAVE A CHAIN SWORD AND 
  POWER GLOVE WHICH REPLACES THE POWER SWORD AND POWER GLOVE. IT HAS 
  THE SAME DICE ROLL AS POWER SWORD AND POWER GLOVE. THIS WEAPON
  CAN ONLY CUT THOUGH WEAKENED HOLES IN WALLS, SIMILAR TO THE 
  POWERSWORD AND GLOVE, AND CAN BE USED DIAGONALLY.

  NEW MARINE WEAPON
  THE ASSAULT CANNON HAS BEEN REPLACED WITH A FLAMER. THE FLAMER
  HAS A SHORT RANGE BUT HAS A WIDE ARC OF FIRE (WHEN THE FIRE ICON
  IS SELECTED A MALTESE CROSS PATTERN APPEARS WHICH IS THE WEAPONS
  FIRIND RANGE). TWO HEAVY WEAPONS DICE ARE ROLLED AND ANY ALIENS 
  OR MARINES WITHIN THE CONE SHAPE OF SQUARES WILL BE HIT WITH THE
  TOTAL OF THE TWO DICE. !

  
